vista.set
Interface DataSet

All Superinterfaces:
Named, java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultDataSet, IndexedDataSet, IrregularTimeSeries, RegularTimeSeries, TimeSeries
public interface DataSet
extends Named, java.io.Serializable

An abstract class for encapsulating DataSet for use in plotting. This would enable different data sets to implement this interface and use the plotting capabilities as long as these functions were properly implemented along with DataSetElement and DataSetIterator
